commit.message: Updated lookup tool to have wildcard support. Usage: % for any number of characters either preceding or following. _ for a single character wildcard. Example: python lookup.py ter%
Added database lookup tool. Usage: lookup.py "word"
Updated AVSplitter to take media and json arguments
Fixed AV Splitter to accurately subdivide clips.
Prelim JSON parsing and media splitting.
Updated with concatenation feature. Will ignore unknown words
Updated Database search to return list of location files
